  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK831">
<l>pētaimai yeṉpatoṉ ṟiyāteṉi ṉētaṅkoṇ</l>
<l>ṭūtiyam pōka viṭal</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Folly is one (of the chief defects) it is that which (makes one) incur loss and forego gain.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
